						<summary>

						<p>Pāṇḍya, Māṟavarman Sundarapāṇḍya I, 8th year = A.D. 1224.</p>						

						<p>Records the setting up of the image of Arundavañjēda-Nāchchiyār by Chēgal-Sēvagattēvaṉ, a member of the <hi rend="italic">Teṉṉilaṅgai-vaḷañjiyar</hi> living in the bazaar Vikkiramapāṇḍiyaṉ-perunderu of Iḍattuvaḷi.</p>						

						<p>[Published in <hi rend="italic">Virudhunagar District Inscriptions</hi>, No. 132/2005.]</p>						

